Reports annotation parameters that are assigned to their `default` value.

Example:


      @interface Test {
          Class<?> expected() default Throwable.class;
      }

      @Test(expected = Throwable.class)
      void testSmth() {}

After the quick-fix is applied:


      @Test()
      void testSmth() {}

